articles.author: Nandita Bose, Andrea Shalal, Jeff Mason
articles.title: In Michigan, Harris meets Arab American leaders angry over Israel - Reuters
articles.description: Vice President Kamala Harris met with Arab American and Muslim leaders in Flint, Michigan, on Friday, as her presidential campaign seeks to win back voters angry at U.S. support for Israel's wars in Gaza and Lebanon.

articles.author: Sara Whitman
articles.title: Donald Glover cancels remainder of Childish Gambino tour dates to get surgery amid mystery illness - Page Six
articles.description: The “This Is America” hitmaker originally postponed his New World Tour in September due to unspecified health issues.
articles.content:
Donald Glover has canceled the remainder of his Childish Gambino New World Tour dates in North America, Europe and the United Kingdom amid a mystery illness.
